<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179405>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 26. Caryanda albomaculata sp. nov. 14. male head and pronotum, dorsal view; 15 – 16. mesosternum and metasternum, male and female; 17 – 18. male terminalia, dorsal and lateral views; 19. female subgenital plate, ventral view; 20. female abdominal apex, lateral view; 21 – 23. epiphallus, dorsal, anterior, and lateral views; 24 – 26. phallic complex, apical, lateral and dorsal views. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179405/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179406>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27 – 31. dorsal and lateral views of body. 27 – 29. Caryanda aurata, sp. nov.; 30 – 31. Caryanda albomaculata sp. nov.; 27 – 28, 30. male; 29, 31. female. (photos of 27, 30 – 31 from fresh specimens; photos of 28 – 29 from dried specimens)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179406/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

